  ${
    $d R u v z $.  $d S u v z $.  $d T u v z $.
    txtop.1 $e |- T = ( R tX S ) $.
    $( The product of two topologies is a topology.  (Contributed by Jeff
       Madsen, 2-Sep-2009.) $)
    txtop $p |- ( ( R e. Top /\ S e. Top ) -> T e. Top ) $=
      ( vz vu vv ctop wcel wa cv cxp wceq wrex cab ctg cfv ctx co txval syl5eq
      ctb txbas tgcl syl eqeltrd ) AHIBHIJZCEKFKGKLMGBNFANEOZPQZHUGABRSUICEGFAB
      TDUAUGUHUBIUIHIEGFABUCUHUDUEUF $.
